    "description": "<p><em><strong>At KABAM Robotics, we believe service robots will free humans to pursue greater purpose. We are driven by our passion to improve lives and empower the service workforce with technology.&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Through our cutting-edge connectivity technologies, and singular focus on user experience, we enable smarter and safer cities, and create a world of seamless connectivity for robots.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Smart+, our proprietary robotic work management system, enables robots to communicate with each other, with building infrastructure and building management system. Our robots are equipped to carry out preemptive AI detections, and deployed as on-the-ground first responders.&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>We have the largest commercial deployments of inspection and security robots in Singapore and are expanding to overseas markets such as Australia and Hong Kong. Our customers are predominantly in the commercial security, facility management, logistics warehouses and hospitality sectors.</strong></em></p>",
